results.t: Wolfgang's Steakhouse: Best Steakhouse in Manila
results.p: The best steakhouse in New York is finally in Manila. Savor the finest dry-aged USDA Prime steaks here at Wolfgang's Steakhouse by Wolfgang Zwiener.
